paragraphs.title: Speed - Merge
paragraphs.text:
SELECT *
FROM lambda.speed_actions_by_site
WHERE site = 'axs.com'
PER PARTITION LIMIT 1;

paragraphs.title: Batch - Merge
paragraphs.text:
SELECT site, 
    MIN(timestamp_bucket) AS timestamp_bucket,
    SUM(comm_count) AS comm_count,
    SUM(fav_count) AS fav_count, 
    SUM(view_count) AS view_count
FROM lambda.batch_actions_by_site
WHERE timestamp_bucket > 1000 AND site = 'axs.com'
GROUP BY site
ALLOW FILTERING;
